These projects can be customize to use in Resume and personal portfolio. In this tutorial you will learn to build modern and complex web apps using React. We will be building 3 react projects. Our first project is Netflix clone using React js. Where we will build the user authentication using Firebase, and we will display the movies details using TMDB API. Our next project is YouTube clone, Where we will build the user interface same as YouTube and we will fetch the video and video details from official YouTube API. Then we will move to third Project using React, where we will build and deploy a crypto price tracking application.
